e":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcfa8be90854c598407308f1dab47b0b57f135f3","tid":2434313,"uid":171399,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T12:25:46.000Z","msg":"忠實廢物 繼續刷鞋啦 <br />\n好快中共直接落嚟管治 到時候你廢物都冇得做 <br />\n陰鳩公"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T17:26:43.000Z","msg":"依家香港建制/政府/中共代理人就係玩緊篤灰.<br />\n係咁篤灰, 推卸責任. 推唔到到最後邊個就俾呀爺殺死.<br />\n<br />\n港澳辦篤建制灰<br />\n好可能係689篤緊AO黨既灰. 突然跳出黎話考慮做特首.<br />\n又瀨蘋果瀨河童<br />\n<br />\n建制要生存, 盲係咁篤泛民 -&gt; 區議. 黎緊唔知有咩篤.<br />\n<br />\n政府林鄭又係度推責任俾建制, 俾下屬.<br />\n<br />\n哇, 呢場大屠殺真係世紀少見."},{"pid":"93bebacdb68f9029cd7288f48d9168cb19c64bd6","tid":2434313,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T17:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁大個人輸唔起"},{"pid":"2b063852d17109d8170d58e3b8713d12ffe43c96","tid":2434313,"uid":49853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T17:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1BFBtHB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1BFBtHB.gif&h=774e47e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949368c19fb60f34e09193b5bd66fc9ab12a49fc","tid":2434313,"uid":360551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T17:36:59.000Z","msg":"佢緊係認為蛇斉餅糉先係區議會功能"},{"pid":"d88b50e679854f6a9326f69830d523f1b253db3f","tid":2434313,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T17:40:26.000Z","msg":"佢會話中共唔啱先出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n哩隻一無是處嘅狗隻只係香港嘅寄生蟲"},{"pid":"0a1c67ca239585e153d67418b7350b7b88fc8b21","tid":2434313,"uid"